options(stringsAsFactors=F)
library(data.table)
library(tidyr)
library(UpSetR)
library(ggplot2)
library(viridis)
rm(list=ls())

sqtl <- fread('data/338Lung_sqtl_5pca.fdr005.batch.txt.gz')
names(sqtl)[1:2] <- c('gene_id','gene')
gen <- read.csv('data/gene_hg19.csv')
sqtl <- left_join(sqtl,gen,by = 'gene_id')
sqtl$gene_id <- substring(sqtl$gene_id,1,15)
sqtl$phe_id <- paste0(sapply(strsplit(sqtl$gene,':'),'[',1),':',sapply(strsplit(sqtl$gene,':'),'[',2),':',sapply(strsplit(sqtl$gene,':'),'[',3),':',sapply(strsplit(sqtl$gene,':'),'[',4),':',sqtl$gene_id)
sqtl$type <- 'sGene'

eqtl <- fread('data/338Lung_eqtl_5pca.fdr005.batch.txt.gz')
eqtl$type <- 'eGene'
eqtl <- left_join(eqtl,gen,by = 'gene_id')
eqtl$gene_id <- substring(eqtl$gene_id,1,15)

aqtl <- fread('data/338Lung_aqtl_5pca.fdr005.batch.txt.gz')
names(aqtl)[1:2] <- c('gene_id','gene')
aqtl <- left_join(aqtl,gen,by = 'gene_id')
aqtl$gene_id <- substring(aqtl$gene_id,1,15)
aqtl$phe_id <- paste0(sapply(strsplit(aqtl$gene,':'),'[',1),':',aqtl$gene_id,':',sapply(strsplit(aqtl$gene,':'),'[',3),':',sapply(strsplit(aqtl$gene,':'),'[',4))
aqtl$type <- 'apaGene'

eqtl <- eqtl[,c('gene_id','type')]
eqtl <- subset(eqtl,!duplicated(gene_id))
aqtl <- aqtl[,c('gene_id','type')]
aqtl <- subset(aqtl,!duplicated(gene_id))
sqtl <- sqtl[,c('gene_id','type')]
sqtl <- subset(sqtl,!duplicated(gene_id))
res <- rbind(eqtl,aqtl,sqtl)
res <- as.data.frame(res)
result <- res %>%
  mutate(value = 1) %>% 
  spread(key = type, value = value, fill = 0)


pdf(file = 'Figure 1A bottom.pdf',width = 5,height = 3)
upset(result, 
      sets = rev(c("apaGene", "eGene", "sGene")),
      keep.order = TRUE, 
      point.size = 3,line.size = 1,
      sets.bar.color = rev(c("#BC3C29", "#2D417F","#CB812A")),
      order.by = "freq",
      mainbar.y.label = "",
      queries = list(
        list(query = function(row) { row["sGene"] == 1 }, color = "#CB812A", active = TRUE),
        list(query = function(row) { row["eGene"] == 1 }, color = "#2D417F", active = TRUE),
        list(query = function(row) { row["apaGene"] == 1 }, color = "#BC3C29", active = TRUE)),
      text.scale = c(1.5, 1.5, 1.2, 1.5, 1.5, 1.5) )
dev.off()

data <- data.frame(
  Category = c("apaGene", "eGene", "sGene"),
  Type = c("APA", "exp", "splicing"),
  Count = c(481, 5560, 1914)
)
data$Category <- factor(data$Category,levels = c("apaGene", "eGene", "sGene"))
custom_colors <- c("#BC3C29", "#2D417F", "#CB812A") 

p <- ggplot(data, aes(x = Category, y = Count, fill = Type)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity", position = position_dodge(width = 0.5), width = 0.5) +
  geom_text(aes(label = Count), 
            position = position_dodge(width = 0.8), 
            vjust = -0.5,hjust = 0.5, size = 5, color = "black") +

  labs(
    x = "",
    y = "Number of genes",
    title = "",
    fill = "Type"
  ) +

    legend.title = element_text(size = 14),

  )
ggsave(p,file='Figure 1A top.pdf',width = 2.5,height = 3)

R
rm(list = ls())
library(data.table)
library(dplyr)
library(ggplot2)
require(gridExtra)
library(ggpubr)
library(tidyverse)

gene_name <- 'IP6K2'
SNP_name <- 'rs1264194'
exp <- fread(paste0(gene_name,'_exp.txt'),data.table = F)
exp <- exp[,-1]
exp <- t(exp)
exp <- cbind(IID=rownames(exp),exp)
exp <- as.data.frame(exp)
names(exp)[2] <- 'eQTL'

query <- fread('../116_geno005_maf001_hwe06.bim_id_query')
head(query)
cbPalette <- c("#0072B5","#0072B5","#0072B5")

gen <- read.table(paste0('338_',SNP_name,'.raw'),h=T,check.names = F)
gen <- subset(gen,!is.na(gen[,ncol(gen)]))
names(gen)[7] <- paste0(query$V7[which(query$V2==sapply(strsplit(names(gen)[7],'_'),'[',1))],'_',sapply(strsplit(names(gen)[7],'_'),'[',2))
allele_last <- sapply(strsplit(names(gen)[7],'_'),'[',1)
allele <- c(sapply(strsplit(allele_last,':'),'[',3),sapply(strsplit(allele_last,':'),'[',4))
alt_allele <- paste0(sapply(strsplit(names(gen)[7],'_'),'[',2),sapply(strsplit(names(gen)[7],'_'),'[',2))
ref_allele <- paste0(setdiff(allele,sapply(strsplit(names(gen)[7],'_'),'[',2)),setdiff(allele,sapply(strsplit(names(gen)[7],'_'),'[',2)))
mix_allele <- paste0(substring(ref_allele,1,1),substring(alt_allele,1,1))

gen$rs_n <- ifelse(gen[,7]==0,paste0(ref_allele,'\n(n=',sum(gen[,7]==0),')'), 
                   ifelse(gen[,7]==2, paste0(alt_allele,'\n(n=',sum(gen[,7]==2),')'),
                          paste0(mix_allele,'\n(n=',sum(gen[,7]==1),')')))

gen$rs_n <- factor(gen$rs_n, levels = c(paste0(ref_allele,'\n(n=',sum(gen[,7]==0),')'), 
                                        paste0(mix_allele,'\n(n=',sum(gen[,7]==1),')'), 
                                        paste0(alt_allele,'\n(n=',sum(gen[,7]==2),')')))

gen <- dplyr::left_join(gen,exp,by = 'IID')
gen[,9] <- as.numeric(gen[,9])

pdui <- fread(paste0(gene_name,'_pdui.txt'),data.table = F)
pdui <- pdui[,-1]
pdui <- t(pdui)
pdui <- cbind(IID=rownames(pdui),pdui)
pdui <- as.data.frame(pdui)
names(pdui)[2] <- 'apaQTL'
psi <- fread(paste0('psi_',gene_name,'_exp.txt'),data.table = F)
psi <- psi[,-1]
psi <- t(psi)
psi <- cbind(IID=rownames(psi),psi)
psi <- as.data.frame(psi)
names(psi)[2] <- 'sQTL'

gen <- dplyr::left_join(gen,pdui,by = 'IID')
gen <- dplyr::left_join(gen,psi,by = 'IID')
gen$apaQTL <- as.numeric(gen$apaQTL)
gen$sQTL <- as.numeric(gen$sQTL)
gen_long <- gen %>%
  pivot_longer(cols = c("apaQTL", "eQTL", "sQTL"),
               names_to = "QTL_type",
               values_to = "value")
cbPalette <- c("CC\n(n=57)" = "#BC3C29", "TC\n(n=157)" = "#2D417F", "TT\n(n=124)" = "#CB812A")  

p <- ggplot(gen_long, aes(x = QTL_type, y = value, fill = rs_n)) +
  geom_violin(position = position_dodge(width = 0.75), alpha = 0.4, trim = TRUE) +
  geom_boxplot(width = 0.2, position = position_dodge(width = 0.75), outlier.shape = NA, alpha = 0.7) +
  stat_summary(fun = median, geom = "point", position = position_dodge(0.75), size = 1.2, color = "black") +
  scale_fill_manual(values = cbPalette) +
  theme_classic() +
  labs(x = "", y = "Normalized gene expression / PDUI / PSI", fill = "Genotype") +
  theme(text = element_text(size = 14),
        axis.text = element_text(size = 14, color = "black"),
        axis.title = element_text(size = 14, color = "black"),
        legend.title = element_text(size = 14),
        legend.text = element_text(size = 14),
        plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5)) +
  ggtitle(paste0("Effects of ", SNP_name,' in cis-xQTLs'))

ggsave(p,filename = 'Figure 1B.pdf',width = 5.5,height = 3.2)

R
rm(list = ls())
library(ggplot2)
library(data.table)
library(dplyr)
rm(list = ls())
eqtl <- read.csv('conditional_eQTL_res.csv')
table(eqtl$independent_qtl)
(5600-4586)/5600 # 0.1810714
aqtl <- read.csv('conditional_aQTL_res.csv')
table(aqtl$independent_qtl)
(665-611)/665 # 0.08120301
sqtl <- read.csv('conditional_sQTL_res.csv')
table(sqtl$independent_qtl)
(4402-3988)/4402 # 0.09404816

df <- data.frame(
  QTL = rep(c("eGene", "aAPA", "sIntron"), each = 2),
  SNP_type = rep(c("Multiple independent effect cis-xQTLs", "Single independent effect cis-xQTL"), times = 3),
  Gene_count = c(5560-4586, 4586, 
                 665-611, 611,
                 4402-3988, 3988))
df$QTL_SNP <- paste(df$SNP_type, df$QTL, sep=" of ")
my_colors <- c(
  "Multiple independent effect cis-xQTLs of eGene" = "#2F6F9B",  
  "Multiple independent effect cis-xQTLs of aAPA"  = "#D62121",  
  "Single independent effect cis-xQTL of aAPA"    = "#BC3C29",  
  "Multiple independent effect cis-xQTLs of sIntron" = "#C69C26", 
  "Single independent effect cis-xQTL of sIntron"   = "#CB812A" )

df$xmin <- ifelse(df$QTL == "sIntron", 2, ifelse(df$QTL == "eGene", 3, 4))
df$xmax <- df$xmin + 0.75  
df$ymin <- 0
df$ymax <- 0
df$fraction <- 0
df[df$QTL=='eGene',]$fraction <- df[df$QTL=='eGene',]$Gene_count/sum(df[df$QTL=='eGene',]$Gene_count)
df[df$QTL=='aAPA',]$fraction <- df[df$QTL=='aAPA',]$Gene_count/sum(df[df$QTL=='aAPA',]$Gene_count)
df[df$QTL=='sIntron',]$fraction <- df[df$QTL=='sIntron',]$Gene_count/sum(df[df$QTL=='sIntron',]$Gene_count)
df[df$QTL=='eGene',]$ymax <- cumsum(df[df$QTL=='eGene',]$fraction)
df[df$QTL=='aAPA',]$ymax <- cumsum(df[df$QTL=='aAPA',]$fraction)
df[df$QTL=='sIntron',]$ymax <- cumsum(df[df$QTL=='sIntron',]$fraction)
df[df$QTL=='eGene',]$ymin <- c(0, head(df[df$QTL=='eGene',]$ymax, n=-1))
df[df$QTL=='aAPA',]$ymin <- c(0, head(df[df$QTL=='aAPA',]$ymax, n=-1))
df[df$QTL=='sIntron',]$ymin <- c(0, head(df[df$QTL=='sIntron',]$ymax, n=-1))

ggplot(df, aes(ymax=ymax, ymin=ymin, xmax=xmax, xmin=xmin, fill=QTL_SNP)) +
  geom_rect(color = "black", size = 0.2) +  
  scale_fill_manual(values = my_colors) +
  coord_polar(theta="y") +  
  xlim(c(1, 5)) + 
  theme_void() +
  theme(legend.position = "top") 

ggsave(filename = 'Figure 1C.pdf',width = 3.5,height = 3.6)

7.1 apaQTL & sQTL replicated in eQTL


cd /data1/qtl/code_for_submit/data/Fig1I

R
library(data.table)
library(tidyverse)
library(qvalue)

aQTL <- fread('338sample_Lung_aqtl_5pca_batch.permute.fdr.txt')
aQTL$gene <- substring(aQTL$gene,1,15)
aQTL$gene_qtl <- paste0(aQTL$gene,':',aQTL$sid)
sQTL <- fread('338sample_sqtl.chunk.permute.chrall.fdr.txt')
sQTL$gene <- substring(sQTL$gene,1,15)
sQTL$gene_qtl <- paste0(sQTL$gene,':',sQTL$sid)
aQTL <- aQTL %>% arrange("gene_qtl", pval_beta)
aQTL <- aQTL[!duplicated(aQTL$gene_qtl),]
aQTL <- subset(aQTL,qval<0.05)
sQTL <- sQTL %>% arrange("gene_qtl", pval_beta)
sQTL <- sQTL[!duplicated(sQTL$gene_qtl),]
